    "summary": "The agent is stuck in a loop of providing meta-commentary or templates because it perceives the lack of input data as a reason to fail, rather than realizing the 'execute' environment will provide the stdin. The prompt needs to shift from 'writing a script' to 'solving the problem via a script' with a stronger emphasis on the fact that input will be provided via stdin."
